    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm just so tired of pretending. there's no point in talking to a therapist about a person who doesn't exist anymore. it's like trying to fix a house that's already burned down to the ground. you just have the ashes left. it feels like there's no reason to stay in the ashes.",
